## 🔄 Common Workflows

### Create Feature Module

1. Update Prisma schema → `pnpm prisma migrate dev --name add_lessons`
2. Create `src/lessons/` with: module, controller, service, repository, dto/
3. Wire up in `app.module.ts`
4. Generate tests

### Add Endpoint

1. Repository:
   `async findByRole(role: string) { return this.prisma.user.findMany({ where: { role } }); }`
2. Service:
   `async findByRole(role: string) { return this.repository.findByRole(role); }`
3. Controller:
   `@Get('by-role/:role') async findByRole(@Param('role') role: string) { ... }`
4. Write tests

### Modify Schema

1. Update `prisma/schema.prisma`
2. `pnpm prisma migrate dev --name description`
3. Update DTOs/entities if needed
4. Update tests

